{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-6", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "緊追猛趕", "storyInfo": "陳林二人突破其他隊伍的包圍來到海邊，眼看已經趕不上，林雨霞使出獨門絕技，成功出線。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不愧是鼠膽龍威隊的兩位女俠，如果是戰鬥的話，她們就絕不會讓人失望！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們輕鬆地解決了圍住她們的人。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，此時第一梯隊已經遊過了一半距離！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鼠膽龍威隊，趕得上嗎？！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "7", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什麼？該游泳了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想一個問題。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼問題？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然我們認為埃內斯托有問題，而他又在我們後面，其實我們應該以他為優先。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有一定道理。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們依然不能確定他就有問題。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，無論這背後是誰，很明顯，對方都不希望我們贏得比賽。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但贏得比賽這個目的太寬泛了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，對方不希望我們上船，我知道。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別廢話了，要輸了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "輸？不可能。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先去吧，好久沒做類似的事了，我要做一些準備。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經過短暫的討論後，不知為何，兩位女俠中，陳女俠先行下水。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而林女俠則留在沙灘上，一邊熱身，一邊似乎在從沙灘上收集沙子。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經知道，林女俠的能力是將沙子變成玻璃作為武器，難道說，她要用沙子在海面上造出一座玻璃大橋？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "largebgtween", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ease": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是爸爸的話，肯定能用這裡的沙子直接變出一座橋來。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我可做不到。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我也有我的方法。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼多沙子應該足夠了。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#7"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳暉潔的位置......正好。", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#7"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......走！", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_